OL,6,FA double killing similar to that of
OL,7,FMichael and Marjorie Cawdery - stabbed
OL,8,Fto death at the hands of a paranoid
OL,9,Fschizophrenic almost eight years ago `
OL,10,Fcould happen again because changes to
OL,11,Favoid such tragedies have ''stalled''.
OL,13,FThat is according to a high-level
OL,14,Fhealth review of an investigation
OL,15,Fcarried out several years ago.
OL,17,FThat review ` to check on the
OL,18,Fimplementation of outstanding
OL,19,Frecommendations ` was drawn up by Dr
OL,20,FSeamus O'Reilly in October 2024.
