OL,6,FThe retired consultant found ''a
OL,7,Fnumber of actions'' have ``stalled''
OL,8,Fwhich ``could potentially result in a
OL,9,Fsimilar incident happening again and
OL,10,Fundermine the confidence of all those
OL,11,Faffected including the public and
OL,12,Fpotentially put staff at risk.''
OL,14,FCharles Little, who was the first to
OL,15,Ffind the bodies of his in-laws at
OL,16,Ftheir home in Portadown back in May
OL,17,F2017, is stunned.
