OL,6,F"They need to get on with action.
OL,7,FAfter seven years from the incident we
OL,8,Fare in the same situation where it
OL,9,Fcould happen again tomorrow or today,
OL,10,Fit is just not acceptable,'' he said.
OL,12,FThe brutal killings of Michael and
OL,13,FMajorie Cawdery in their own home in
OL,14,FPortadown in May 2017 stunned the
OL,15,Flocal community and beyond.
OL,17,FThe man responsible for the frenzied
OL,18,Fattack ` Thomas McEntee ` was jailed
OL,19,Ffor a minimum of 10 years.
