OL,6,FHe had been in contact with health
OL,7,Fofficials and police in Belfast and
OL,8,FCraigavon in the run-up and on the day
OL,9,Fof the killings.
OL,11,FPolice and the Department of Health
OL,12,Fhave apologised for the damning
OL,13,Ffailures in the case.
OL,15,FIn December 2023, an inquest found the
OL,16,Fpensioners deaths were ''entirely
OL,17,Fpreventable''.
OL,19,FThe findings of the review, obtained
OL,20,Fby UTV, also focused on what staff had
OL,21,Fto say on the frontline.
