OL,6,FIt also outlines claims that since the
OL,7,Ffirst investigation into what
OL,8,Fhappened, almost ten similar incidents
OL,9,Fhave already occurred.
OL,11,F''They make it seem like Mike and
OL,12,FMajorie's death, which we had hoped
OL,13,Fwould be a watershed, where things
OL,14,Fwhere change, but it seems as if it it
OL,15,Fdoesn't matter to them, it is just
OL,16,Fanother exercise in paperwork,''
OL,17,FCharles Little said.
