OL,6,FA statement from the Department said:
OL,7,F"In the years after the tragic deaths
OL,8,Fof Mr and Mrs Cawdrey, all HSC Trusts
OL,9,Fhave worked together to understand how
OL,10,Fthis happened and what can be done to
OL,11,Fminimise risk going forward.
OL,13,F"In the autumn of 2024, the HSC wished
OL,14,Fto assess the progress achieved in
OL,15,Fmaking our system safer. An
OL,16,Findependent review was commissioned.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/11
