OL,6,F"An early draft of the report was
OL,7,Fshared with Mr Little so that Mr and
OL,8,FMrs Cawdrey's family experience could
OL,9,Fbe included. Mr and Mrs Little kindly
OL,10,Fcontinue to meet with Departmental
OL,11,Fofficials to support this process.
OL,13,F"UTV states that it has had sight of
OL,14,Fan early confidential draft of this
OL,15,Findependent review, however the fact-
OL,16,Fchecking process is still in progress
OL,17,Fand has not yet been completed.
