OL,6,F"Whilst the Health Minister and
OL,7,FDepartment remain grateful for the
OL,8,Finput from Mr Little and welcome his
OL,9,Fviews, we cannot comment on the
OL,10,Fcontent of a draft report at this
OL,11,Fstage.
OL,13,F"The Health Minister has previously
OL,14,Fmet Mr Little to discuss his concerns
OL,15,Fand the Department is committed to
OL,16,Ffurther engagement with families on
OL,17,Fthese important patient safety issues.
