OL,6,F"Serious Adverse Incident (SAI)
OL,7,Freviews are a fundamental part of how
OL,8,Fthe whole Health and Social Care
OL,9,Fsystem should learn from harm and make
OL,10,Fimprovements to the systems for the
OL,11,Fdelivery of safe patient care.
OL,13,F"A redesign of the current SAI
OL,14,Fprocedure is progressing. The aim of
OL,15,Fthe Redesign Programme is to deliver a
OL,16,Fnew regional Framework to deliver
OL,17,Flearning and improvement from Patient
OL,18,FSafety Incidents across the HSC.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/11
