OL,6,F"The Framework aims to deliver a more
OL,7,Fstreamlined, simpler and proportionate
OL,8,Fresponse to Patient Safety Incidents
OL,9,Fwith an emphasis on learning,
OL,10,Fcompassionately engaging and
OL,11,Fsupporting all those involved and
OL,12,Fsystem improvement and change, framed
OL,13,Fwithin a culture which prioritises
OL,14,Fsafety, openness and compassion.
